org.batfish.datamodel

Class IcmpCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.IcmpCode

  • public final class IcmpCode
extends Object
    Represents the integer constants used for ICMP Codes. For more information, see RFC-792, RFC-1122, RFC-1812, and more.
